
                 Zetris v1.0 Documentation (rel. 17-Jan-93)
                 ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

                                Requirements
                                ~~~~~~~~~~~~
                   Amiga OS1.2/1.3/2.0/3.0/4.0 or Higher
                             diskfont.library 
                         Courier 13 Font (Supplied)
                           One Free Audio Channel
             Approx. 20kb Free Public Mem and 1kb Free Chip Mem
                640*256/68020/OS2.0 Combination Recommended

                               Zetris History
                               ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
                   08-Jun-92 v1.0 (What a Piece of Crap!)


                                    Keys
                                    ~~~~
                  '4' or 'D' ............ Move Brick Left
                  '6' or 'G' ........... Move Brick Right
                  '5' or 'F' ..... Rotate Brick Clockwise
                  [Space] ................. Release Brick

                  'S' ........................ Start Game
                  'P' ........................ Pause Game
                  'T' ............. Toggle Beeping On/Off
                  '0' ............ Set Task Priority to 0
                  '1' ............ Set Task Priority to 1
                  '2' ............ Set Task Priority to 2
                  '3' ............ Set Task Priority to 5


